REST API AUTOMATION

1. Create Maven Project with Cucumber and rest assured dependencies
2. Define Project structure with Cucumber and rest Assured dependencies
3. Create a Feature file with the test case you want to automate
4. Implement smart step definitions files with supported code
5. build util files to define all reusable request and responses
6. Can print the request and response log by using addFilter method
7. Define global properties and drive all the global variables from properties file
8. Define dynamic json in feature file using example keyword
   when we use example keyword Scenario should be outline
9. Implement parameterization to run tests with multiple data sets
10.Devlop end-to-end functionality Test with all validation and assertions
